TERMS AND CONDITIONS OF USE OF THE "LALIGA FANTASY" GAME
1.- OWNERSHIP AND PURPOSE
These terms and conditions regulate the terms of use (hereinafter, the "
Terms
") of the LALIGA Fantasy game in its app and web version (hereinafter, the "
Game"
) by the users of the same. Said Game is exclusively owned by LaLiga Group International, S.L., with Tax ID number B05421805 and registered office in Madrid, C/ Torrelaguna 60, 28043 (hereinafter, "
LALIGA
").
LALIGA is a company duly incorporated under the laws of Spain and is majority owned by the Liga Nacional de Fútbol Profesional. For more information about LALIGA please access the
Legal Notice
.
LALIGA provides the Game free of charge for those users who wish to play, consisting of a football manager where they can create virtual leagues to play with other users, the objective being to score as many points as possible. The score is obtained from the sum of the points obtained by each player lined up in each match day of the National First Division League Championship. Points are awarded to each player according to a series of criteria, including goals, yellow and red cards, among others.
IF THE USER HAS ANY COMMENTS, QUESTIONS OR REQUESTS PLEASE SEND AN EMAIL TO THE FOLLOWING ADDRESS: support@laligafantasy.zendesk.com
This Game has been developed to be used on mobile devices with iOS, Android OS, Windows Phone or other similar operating systems, and LALIGA can periodically update it.
2.- USER
The registration and creation of an account (hereinafter, the "
Account
") in order to use the Game automatically confers the status of user (hereinafter, "
User
") on the person who does so, and implies acceptance of and compliance with the Terms. In accordance with the above, the User is obliged to read these Terms, as well as any other conditions that regulate the use and enjoyment of the Game or its environment, before using or enjoying the Game. You may save these Terms or print them for future reference. LALIGA will also save the text of the entire contract and make it available to you on request.
The User is aware and voluntarily and expressly accepts that the use of the Game is in any case under his sole and exclusive responsibility.
Minimum age.
In order to register and use the Game you must be at least sixteen (16) years of age or have your parent's and/or legal guardian's permission to register and use the Game. Therefore, by accepting these Terms you warrant that you are at least sixteen (16) years of age or, if you are not, that you have parental consent to register for the Game and you accept full responsibility for this statement.
LALIGA may contact the User, at any time, to prove their real age by providing a photocopy of their National Identity Document or an equivalent document. In the event that the User does not provide the aforementioned documentation, LALIGA reserves the right to block the User's use of the Game.
Registration and single sign-on service (LALIGA Single Sign-On).
LALIGA has implemented a means of registration and single sign-on (LALIGA Single Sign-On) that allows the User to access an environment created by LALIGA (LALIGA Ecosystem) and integrated by several applications and websites, both of LALIGA and of the affiliated football clubs with which LALIGA has collaboration agreements, with the aim that the User can enjoy a series of advantages. Each user receives a unique identifier so that any selection or modification of preferences or deletion request made in one of the applications or websites that are part of the ecosystem will affect the rest of the LALIGA Ecosystem environment and the entities that comprise it.
Through LALIGA Single Sign-On, a unique "fan profile" is created in all the channels (assets) connected to LALIGA Ecosystem, which is shared by all the entities responsible for these assets (LALIGA apps and websites, affiliated clubs' apps and websites, etc.).
For more information on LALIGA Ecosystem please consult the following web link:
https://www.laliga.com/informacion-legal/laliga-ecosistema
.
3.- GENERAL CONDITIONS OF USE
3.1.- Registration: login and password
In order to be able to use and enjoy the Game, the User must register by providing the data required to validate the registration. In order to register, the instructions included in the registration form must be followed using the forms provided in the Registration option.
All the information provided by the User through the forms presented to access the functionalities of the Game for the aforementioned purposes or any other, must be truthful, and specifically, the User must be the owner of the e-mail address provided. To this effect, the User guarantees the authenticity of all the data that he/she provides, and that he/she will keep the information provided perfectly updated so that it corresponds, at all times, to the real situation of the User. In any case, the User will be solely responsible for any false or inaccurate statements made and for any damages caused to LALIGA or third parties as a result of the information provided.
When the User creates a User Account, he/she is given a user name and password (hereinafter referred to as "
Identifiers
") that he/she specifies, which will enable him/her to access his/her private Account. The Identifiers are personal and confidential. They can only be changed at the User's request or at LALIGA's initiative. For security purposes, the User undertakes to ensure that the password chosen to register for the Game is unique, i.e. that it is not used for any other application, e-mail account or similar. The assigned identifiers will be personal and non-transferable, and may not be transferred, even temporarily, to third parties. In this sense, the User undertakes to make diligent use of and to keep secret his or her assigned Identifiers, if applicable, to access the Game and/or the Content. In the event that the User knows or suspects the loss, theft or use of his/her password or confidential Identifiers by third parties, he/she must inform LALIGA as soon as possible.
The User will be able to select a preferred region to play (Spain or Global). This choice will imply differences in the content and functionalities of the game. For example, only in the game mode of the Spain region, users will be eligible to participate in the Sponsored Leagues and will have the possibility to watch DAZN's ‘partidazo’ every matchday. LALIGA therefore recommends users to choose the Spain region only if they reside in Spain as the prizes of the Competitions and Contests of the Sponsored Leagues can only be awarded to users in this territory.
The User shall be liable for the costs and damages caused by the access and use of the Game and/or the Content by any third party using User Identifiers for this purpose due to the non-diligent use or wilful loss of the User Identifiers.
3.2.- Other associated accounts
For certain aspects of the Game, you may be able to set up additional accounts that are dependent on your account ("associated account(s)"). The User agrees to be bound by these Terms for any associated accounts (including those of minors) that the User now has or subsequently creates, and that the User is responsible for all activity that occurs under his/her account and any associated account(s). You agree that LALIGA may take action against your account in response to activity on any of your associated accounts, including (i) limiting who may use your Game account or any associated account; (ii) limiting the number of devices from which you may access the Game; (iii) and/or deleting your Account or any associated account.
If you permit or authorise a minor to use an associated account:
The User declares that he/she is a parent or legal guardian of the minor;
The User agrees to supervise the use of the Game by minors who are permitted or authorised by the User to use the Game. The Game is not intended for use by children under the age of sixteen (16) without adult supervision;
If using an associated account, the User acknowledges that the Account holder has full control over its associated account. This control includes the right to: (i) terminate use and enjoyment of the Game; (ii) close or alter their associated account at any time; (iii) access or modify the Parental Controls for their associated account; and (iv) receive notifications from LALIGA. In some cases, this control also includes the ability to request and receive device usage information and Game services in relation to your associated account. Collect profile, usage and activity data relating to your associated account and send it to the account holder of the Game services.
