3.9.- Premium Access with Tokens
The Game may include the option to purchase one-time payment tokens that allow the User to access new functionalities or enhancements within it. Tokens are a one-time payment and not a subscription. The price of tokens is set at the time of purchase and is not subject to change for that specific purchase.
LALIGA reserves the right to modify the price of tokens for future purchases due to changes in market conditions, significant increases in acquisition or service provision costs, or in the case of variations in VAT or any other similar tax. Price changes will be reflected directly in the Application and will be effective for purchases made after the price change date. No prior notification to users will be required for token price changes, as these do not involve recurring payments or subscriptions.
3.10.- Subscriptions
The Game includes paid subscriptions that allow the User to enjoy LALIGA Fantasy without advertising. By paying a monthly fee, the User will be able to use the Game without having to watch advertisements.
Subscriptions are open to users of legal age who reside in Spain. To do so, it will be necessary to have a credit or debit card with a Spanish bank or linked to the iTunes account.
Payment will be made through the account associated with the User's device, either App Store or Google Play. It is necessary to have a credit/debit card associated with the account.
The subscription to the ad-free Game will be charged once a month, on or around the day on which the User subscribes. If the billing date is scheduled for a day that does not exist in every month (e.g. the 31st), it will be charged on the last day of that month.
The subscription will be renewed automatically. In case the user does not want the subscription to be renewed automatically, the user will have to cancel the subscription at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. The renewal will be charged on the same day the subscription starts.
The User may cancel their subscription and continue to enjoy LALIGA Fantasy with advertisements by accessing their account settings on their device, accessing the purchased subscription and requesting cancellation.
To request a refund of a subscription, it will depend on:
If the User made a subscription request from an iOS device, the User must access the URL: https://support.apple.com/es-es/HT204084 and request a refund. You must first confirm whether the purchased product is eligible for a refund under Apple's refund policies.
If the User made a subscription request from an ANDROID device and you wish to withdraw, you can request a refund within the first 48 hours by accessing your account settings. You can find more information at:
https://support.google.com/googleplay/workflow/9813244?p=refundAWF&visit_id=637768946016484052-2789740922&rd=1
